'''2003年墨尔本杯'''是[[墨爾本盃|墨尔本杯]]的143屆賽事。赛事於2003年11月4日在[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]的[[費明頓馬場|費明頓馬場]]举行，途程是3200米的草地賽。赛事吸引了122,736人入場觀賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.flemington.com.au/racing/track-records-and-attendances|title=Track records and Attendances|work=Flemington.com.au|accessdate=4 November 2020|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320224301/https://www.flemington.com.au/racing/track-records-and-attendances}}</ref>

五岁馬[[戴花|戴花]]赢得冠军。此馬的練馬師是[[賀賢|賀賢]]，騎師是薄奇能。 <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://horsebetting.com.au/who-won-the-2003-melbourne-cup/158079/ |title=2003 Melbourne Cup result |access-date=2021-04-05 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116171941/https://horsebetting.com.au/who-won-the-2003-melbourne-cup/158079/ }}</ref>

